<cb:div>
<pb n="0094a" xml:id="I01.0038.0094a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 38</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>僧演造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0094a0101">郭世貴一心供養
<lb ed="I" n="0094a02" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a03" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a04" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a05" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a06" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a07" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a08" type="honorific"/>清信駱花嬰
<lb ed="I" n="0094a09" type="honorific"/>一心供養佛時</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0094b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0094b0101">夫大覺神<note n="0094001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨕞＝遷【史】</note><app n="0094001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨕞</rdg></app>。非經像無以表其
<lb ed="I" n="0094b02" type="honorific"/>真。益世閏時。<note n="0094002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠗦＝憑【史】</note><app n="0094002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">憑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠗦</rdg></app>形<note n="0094003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">筫＝質【史】</note><app n="0094003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">質</lem><rdg wit="【原】">筫</rdg></app>如<note n="0094004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30627"/>＝取【史】</note><app n="0094004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">取</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30627"/></rdg></app>利。然
<lb ed="I" n="0094b03" type="honorific"/>僧<note n="0094005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30633"/>＝演【史】</note><app n="0094005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">演</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30633"/></rdg></app>減割衣鉢之資。造石像壹
<lb ed="I" n="0094b04" type="honorific"/>區。金像三區。<note n="0094006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">泘＝浮【史】</note><app n="0094006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">浮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">泘</rdg></app><note n="0094007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30629"/>＝圖【史】</note><app n="0094007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30629"/></rdg></app>三級。大般<note n="0094008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30630"/>＝涅【史】</note><app n="0094008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">涅</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30630"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0094b05" type="honorific"/>槃經<note n="0094009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30631"/>＝兩【史】</note><app n="0094009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兩</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30631"/></rdg></app>部。雜經三百<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">品</unclear>。供養僧
<lb ed="I" n="0094b06" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">卅</unclear>人。上為　<note n="0094010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">国＝國【史】</note><app n="0094010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">國</lem><rdg wit="【原】">国</rdg></app>主。百僚。師徒<note n="0094011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30632"/>＝所【史】</note><app n="0094011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30632"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0094b07" type="honorific"/>生。法界之<note n="0094012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30635"/>＝類【史】</note><app n="0094012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">類</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30635"/></rdg></app>。咸同正覺。
<lb ed="I" n="0094b08" type="honorific"/>大統四年。<note n="0094013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">嵗＝歲【史】</note><app n="0094013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">嵗</rdg></app>次<note n="0094014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">弍＝戊【史】</note><app n="0094014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">弍</rdg></app>午。七月十五
<lb ed="I" n="0094b09" type="honorific"/>日。比丘僧<app type="star" corresp="#0094005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">演</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30633"/></rdg></app>敬造供養。</p>
</cb:div>
